ratings.comment: Stacie is an amazing professor that is willing to help all of her students learn. She is very knowledgeable and proves it during lectures. I would recommend watching the online lectures before in person lectures to gain a better understanding of the material. The class is challenging but Stacie makes the class enjoyable and interesting!

Stacie is one of the best professors I've ever had! She is incredibly caring and truly wants her students to succeed. Going to office hours is very helpful. Corporate tax is a very hard class but she makes it really interesting and overall is just the best! Definitely recommend taking courses with her

Stacie is incredible. She cares so much about her student's understanding of course material. Corporate tax is extremely difficult, so Stacie still expects a ton out of her students. Your life will be much better by taking this class. If you are willing to work hard, the class will be a blast.

Stacie is one of the best professor I have met and she really cares about if students can truly learn from her class. The engaging lecture enhanced my understanding of materials and saved more time before the exam. If you are doing a tax track, her class will also help you perform well on the advanced corporation class, as well as the CPA exam!

Stacie is an extremely knowledgable and engaging lecturer. While this class is tough, she cares about her students and wants them to learn. She's very accessible and approachable outside of class and is willing to lend advice outside of corporate tax. Take this class if you plan on taking the CPA!
Great teacher, engages you during lecture, gives you notes to follow along. Similar to Al's class except tests are closed note.
